    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the <strong>tofu</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tofu</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and set aside to marinate</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated tofu</strong> to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>into quarters, then separate the quarters so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> in a small bowl with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>tofu</strong> to a plate and set aside</p><p>Return the pan to the heat and add the <strong>onion petals</strong> and <strong>halved green beans</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>crispy tofu</strong> and <strong>sweet chilli sauce </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up until it's all coated in the sauce</p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened \u2013 this is your <strong>plant-based sweet chilli tofu stir fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-sweet-chilli-tofu-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>plant-based sweet chilli tofu stir fry</strong> with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
